SimplePoiDesc::SimplePoiDesc (  const ServerTileMapFormatDesc &  tmfd,
const MC2String &  urlbase,
const POIImageIdentificationTable &  imageTable
) 
 

Creates a new SimplePoiDesc from the ServerTileMapFormatDesc.

Is self-contained in opposit of the SimplePoiMaps, i.e. you can still use the objects when the ServerTileMapFormatDesc has been deleted.

Parameters:
tmfd ServerTileMapFormatDesc
urlbase The base url to be added before all the images when fetching via HTTP, e.g. "/TMap/"
imageTable Special POI image table for custom pois.
